==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unclog
<hw>Un*clog"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>clog</ets>.]</ety> <def>To disencumber of a clog, or of
difficulties and obstructions; to free from encumbrances; to set at
liberty.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

